data.description: Price reduction on this lovely 2-story home. Why wait to build when this 2 year old home on an oversized fully fenced lot is here and ready to move in.  Barely lived in, downstairs is an open floor plan with a gourmet kitchen featuring double ovens, granite counter tops, more than enough counter space & cabinets.  Center Island overlooks the spacious, private backyard.  The half bath, breakfast nook and living area complete this level, making it perfect for entertaining or relaxing evenings at home.  Upstairs you will find a loft, 2 large guest bedrooms with a shared bath along with a large primary bedroom, ensuite bath offers both a soaking tub and separate shower.  The walk-in closet has to been seen to be believed. The home offers more privacy than most homes in a subdivision, so it is a must see!  Easy commute to NAS Jax, and close to all the shopping and amenities of Fleming Island, boat launches to the St. Johns River and Orange Park.
